<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.6">
<l>entā taitātaiyappā leḻuvarpa ḻavaṭimai</l>
<l>vantā reṉeñciṉuḷḷē vantāyaip pōkaloṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>antō veṉṉāruyirē yaracēya ruḷeṉakku</l>
<l>nantā maltantaventāy naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My father’s father and beyond those of seven [generations]</l>
<l>Were born to hereditary service. You who came into my heart,</l>
<l>I cannot allow [your] going, oh no, you who are my precious life, [my] king,</l>
<l>My father who gave me grace without stinting, O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
